title: ParaSwap Safety Module - Liquidity Component 🛡️🌊
body:
This proposal suggests adding a layer to ParaSwap’s Safety Module. Unlike the first two ones, this layer will be funded by user deposits incentivized by a PSP budget supplied from the Ecosystem Reserve. It will help to further establish ParaSwap as the safest DEX aggregator, as well as diversify and grow PSP’s liquidity.

Make sure to understand the proposal before expressing your vote.

The current Safety Module (two layers) is documented here: https://doc.paraswap.network/psp-token-and-governance/fees-usage-safety-module

You’ll find additional information about this proposal in the following post: https://medium.com/paraswap/paraswap-safety-module-liquidity-component-%EF%B8%8F-11baea5c8147
